animation:fadeUp .6s .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) forwards}.cover .cover-details{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);animation:fadeUp .6s .9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) forwards}@keyframes fadeUp{to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}.flow-step,.scope-item,.term-item,.roi-stat,.step-card,.case-study{transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),border-color .3s,box-shadow .3s}.flow-step:hover,.scope-item:hover,.term-item:hover,.step-card:hover,.case-study:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--green);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,230,118,.08)}.roi-stat:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--green);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,230,118,.08)}.roi-stat:hover .roi-stat-value{text-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(0,230,118,.4)}.investment-box{transition:border-color .3s,box-shadow .3s}.investment-box:hover{box-shadow:0 0 48px rgba(0,230,118,.15)}.btn-primary{transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}.btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,230,118,.3)}.btn-secondary{transition:border-color .2s,color .2s}.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green)}.timeline-table tr{transition:background .2s}.timeline-table tr:hover{background:rgba(0,230,118,.03)}.cover-nav{opacity:0;animation:fadeIn .8s .1s forwards}@keyframes fadeIn{to{opacity:1}}.payment-section{opacity:0;transform:scale(.96);transition:opacity .7s,transform .7s}.payment-section.visible{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"scroll-progress\"></div><div class=\"dot-bg\"></div>\n<div class=\"cover\"><div class=\"cover-nav\"><div class=\"logo\"><div class=\"logo-mark\">IM</div><span class=\"logo-text\">Iván Manfredi</span></div><span class=\"cover-meta\">PROPOSAL / March 2, 2026</span></div><div class=\"cover-tag\">AI &amp; Automation Architect</div><h1>Batch Invoice Automation System</h1><p class=\"cover-sub\">A custom-built system to eliminate manual processes and replace operational drag with immutable infrastructure for .</p><div class=\"cover-details\"><div class=\"cover-detail\"><span class=\"cover-detail-label\">Prepared For</span><span class=\"cover-detail-value\">Romae Blair</span></div><div class=\"cover-detail\"><span class=\"cover-detail-label\">Company</span><span class=\"cover-detail-value\"></span></div><div class=\"cover-detail\"><span class=\"cover-detail-label\">Delivery</span><span class=\"cover-detail-value\">4 weeks</span></div> <div class=\"cover-detail\"><span class=\"cover-detail-label\">Investment</span><span class=\"cover-detail-value\">$5000</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><span class=\"section-number\">01 / The Problem</span><h2>What's Costing You Time</h2><p> is currently losing productivity to manual processes that don't scale. Based on our discovery conversations:</p><div class=\"problem-card\"><p>Invoices are currently generated one at a time with no batch capability, causing overtime for international shipments. System limitations cap output at ~10 invoices per day with no branding, customization, or proper information transfer.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><span class=\"section-number\">02 / The Solution</span><h2>What We're Building</h2><p>An automated pipeline that takes structured invoice data from GHL, generates dynamic branded HTML using AI, and converts it to print-ready PDF in batch  -  reusable across multiple aerospace companies with minimal reconfiguration.</p><p>Using <strong>n8n</strong> as the automation backbone, integrated with GHL (GoHighLevel) / eliminating manual touchpoints while giving you full control.</p> <h3>System Flow</h3><div class=\"flow-grid\"><div class=\"flow-step\"><span class=\"flow-step-number\">Step 01</span><div class=\"flow-step-title\">Trigger</div><div class=\"flow-step-desc\">GHL sub-account webhook triggers batch processing when the team initiates batch invoice generation</div></div> <div class=\"flow-step\"><span class=\"flow-step-number\">Step 02</span><div class=\"flow-step-title\">Process</div><div class=\"flow-step-desc\">n8n webhook listener receives the trigger, pulls all pending invoices from GHL via API, loops through each invoice, uses AI (Claude or OpenAI) to generate dynamic branded HTML per invoice, then converts HTML to print-ready PDF via pdf.co with multi-page pagination and error handling</div></div> <div class=\"flow-step\"><span class=\"flow-step-number\">Step 03</span><div class=\"flow-step-title\">Output</div><div class=\"flow-step-desc\">Branded, multi-page commercial invoices as clean PDFs delivered in batch (storage location TBD  -  GHL, Google Drive, email, or combination)</div></div> <div class=\"flow-step\"><span class=\"flow-step-number\">Step 04</span><div class=\"flow-step-title\">Notify</div><div class=\"flow-step-desc\">Completion notification with batch summary report  -  X generated, Y failed, with failure reasons. Failed invoices flagged in GHL for manual review.</div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><span class=\"section-number\">03 / Scope of Work</span><h2>What's Included</h2><div class=\"scope-grid\"><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>Discovery call with stepdad to map invoice fields</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>GHL sub-account setup and configuration</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>n8n batch automation workflow</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>AI prompt engineering for HTML generation</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>pdf.co integration and PDF output</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>Error handling and logging</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>Multi-page pagination logic</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>Branded template (one company)</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>Architecture and workflow documentation</div><div class=\"scope-item\"><div class=\"scope-check\">✓</div>New company onboarding guide</div></div><h3>Not Included</h3><p>ERP or third-party system integrations, client-facing portals, multiple company setups (Phase 1 is one company only), ongoing maintenance after support period, GHL subscription costs, pdf.co subscription costs, and AI API usage costs.</p></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><span class=\"section-number\">04 / Timeline</span><h2>Delivery Schedule</h2><table class=\"timeline-table\"><thead><tr><th>Phase</th><th>Duration</th><th>Deliverable</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"phase-name\">Discovery and field mapping</td><td class=\"phase-duration\">1 week</td><td class=\"phase-deliverable\">Call with stepdad to map invoice fields and requirements</td></tr><tr><td class=\"phase-name\">GHL setup and n8n workflow build</td><td class=\"phase-duration\">2 weeks</td><td class=\"phase-deliverable\">Configured GHL sub-account and n8n batch automation workflow</td></tr><tr><td class=\"phase-name\">AI prompt engineering and PDF generation</td><td class=\"phase-duration\">1 week</td><td class=\"phase-deliverable\">AI-powered dynamic HTML generation and pdf.co PDF conversion</td></tr><tr><td class=\"phase-name\">Testing, QA, edge cases</td><td class=\"phase-duration\">1 week</td><td class=\"phase-deliverable\">Fully tested batch invoice system with edge case handling</td></tr><tr><td class=\"phase-name\">Documentation and handoff</td><td class=\"phase-duration\">1 week</td><td class=\"phase-deliverable\">Architecture overview, workflow documentation, and new company onboarding guide</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"timeline-total\">Total: 4 weeks</div></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><span class=\"section-number\">05 / Investment</span><h2>Pricing</h2><div class=\"investment-box\"><div class=\"investment-price\"><span class=\"investment-currency\">$</span> 5000</div><div class=\"investment-model\">Fixed project fee</div><div class=\"investment-terms\"><div class=\"